Happy Birthday to the most incredible woman I know! This past year has been a whirlwind of love, growth, and pure magic all thanks to you. Watching you embrace motherhood with such grace, strength, and love has been nothing short of inspiring. Your dedication, nurturing spirit, and unwavering love for our little munchkins Keith, Ziggy & Ollie makes me so happy. Even as you’ve taken on this new role, your light hasn’t dimmed one bit – you remain the same incredible, caring, and beautiful person I fell in love with. Here’s to celebrating you, not just as an amazing mom, but as the extraordinary woman you’ve always been. Happy First Year as a Mom and Happy Birthday, my love! I love you so much!
